Load Packages
```{r}
install.packages("tidyverse")
install.packages("readxl")
install.packages("janitor")

library(tidyverse)
library(readxl)
library(janitor)

```

Import Data
```{r}
Spring_2020_Percent_Cover_Raw_Data <- read_excel("Spring 2020 - Percent Cover - Raw Data DNET.xlsx", sheet = "Sheet1", col_names = FALSE)

glimpse(Spring_2020_Percent_Cover_Raw_Data)
```

Name columns after a row
```{r}
Spring_2020_Percent_Cover_Raw_Data <- Spring_2020_Percent_Cover_Raw_Data %>% row_to_names(row_number(1))
```


Rename Col Names
```{r}
Spring_2020_Percent_Cover_Raw_Data <- Spring_2020_Percent_Cover_Raw_Data %>%  rename(Transect = `Transect #`,  Hits = `# Hits`)
```
